{"tid":2060402,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"亞馬遜暫停美警使用人臉識辨技術一年","createTime":"2020-06-11T15:14:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T15:28:00.000Z","uid":1086,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"538f8aea5e093a2c09bc43b9860fbf6342a04ee7","tid":2060402,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:14:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2665000/2668086/AFP20180123_257958_01_03_1024_1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2665000%2F2668086%2FAFP20180123_257958_01_03_1024_1024_1024.jpg&h=96ecdb17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n世界各地人民對警暴問題都十分關注，美國警民衝擊不斷升溫的背景下，美國科網巨頭亞馬遜（美：AMZN）突然宣布將暫停授權美國警方使用亞馬遜旗下的人臉識辨系統「Rekognition」一年。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，在亞馬遜作出相關舉動前，近日另一美國科技焦點公司IBM（美：IBM）亦已宣布將不會出售人臉識辨系統，同時亦不會繼續進行相關研發。<br />\n<br />\n亞馬遜沒有明確指出不再授權美國警方使用「Rekognition」的原因，惟外界早已非議亞馬遜向官方售賣人臉識辨技術，憂市民大眾的私隱受到破壞，同時令有色人種受到的監控加劇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2668086/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2668086%2F&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0ohgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=50d281c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2668086/</a>"},{"pid":"34564c696ae2262fadb2725f4c7ead58f887b873","tid":2060402,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:19:17.000Z","msg":"賣去中國，fatfat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce2c4d414314290fd6c8b4265cd854827d15517d","tid":2060402,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34564c696ae2262fadb2725f4c7ead58f887b873","tid":2060402,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:19:17.000Z","msg":"賣去中國，fatfat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />